\t\t<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">Ravindra Rao, our founder, is a renowned expert in the financial markets with over 20 years of experience working with some of the top broking firms. His robust educational background includes an MBA in Finance, a Chartered Market Technician (CMT) and Certified Financial Technician (CFTe) both the credential from the USA, and an EPAT\u2122 (Executive Program in Algorithmic Trading) certification.<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\">Ravindra is celebrated for his deep understanding of financial analysis and market dynamics. His insights are frequently sought after by leading business news channels such as CNBC, ET Now, and Zee Business, where he shares his expertise on prevailing market trends and investment strategies. Ravindra&#8217;s contributions to print media further establish him as a thought leader in the industry, making his knowledge accessible to a broader audience.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1ba7426 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1ba7426\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1c0b6fb elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1c0b6fb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.21.0 - 26-05-2024 *\/\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"310\" height=\"310\" src=\"https:\/\/arthavrksh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-06-12-at-11.31.40.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-514\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/